The '''ropeswing''' is a rope hanging from a long branched tree on an [[Ogre]] island located west of [[Yanille]]. [[Grew]], [[Ogre]]s, and several [[jangerberries]] can be found on the island. Players can access the island by using a [[Rope|rope]] on the branch on the western long branched tree. This will require an [[Agility]] level of 10. The rope will not be returned and no [[Experience|experience]] will be awarded. The island can be left by using the northern ropeswing with a permanent rope. Doing so will grant the player 3 experience in [[Agility]].
